01:28.414 --> 01:30.349
He's meeting
my husband tomorrow.

01:30.383 --> 01:32.484
Here in Beirut.

01:32.519 --> 01:33.853
You can kill them both.

01:33.887 --> 01:35.254
SAUL: I didn't want her here
in the first place.

01:35.289 --> 01:36.723
She's not well.

01:36.757 --> 01:38.291
<i>I don't know if</i>
<i>this woman's for real</i>

